{"type":"message","id":"46c84f24","parentId":"74252fd3","timestamp":"2026-04-05T04:14:30.094Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron event trigger for a scheduled Memory Keeper task. The system is telling me that the memory keeper organization task has been executed.\n\nAccording to my instructions:\n1. This is a heartbeat/cron event - I should check HEARTBEAT.md\n2. The reminder content says \"Memory Keeper 整理任务已执行\" (Memory Keeper organization task has been executed)\n3. I should handle this internally and not relay to the user unless explicitly requested\n\nLet me check what's in HEARTBEAT.md to see if there are any specific actions I should take.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_086f55be15fa4f7cb43fb9ba","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":10224,"output":154,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775362467238,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ddfe639f-cde3-4182-81d9-59054f4dadd1"}}
