{"type":"message","id":"dab0a09f","parentId":"82409fe5","timestamp":"2026-04-05T04:16:21.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to check/test my coding abilities. They want me to first answer them about my coding capabilities.\n\nLet me respond by describing my coding capabilities based on the tools available to me.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的！让我介绍一下我的代码能力 🦐\n\n## 🔧 我的代码能力\n\n### 核心能力\n- **文件操作**: 读取、编写、编辑文件（支持所有主流语言）\n- **Shell 执行**: 运行命令、脚本，支持 PTY（终端交互）\n- **代码调试**: 执行代码、检查输出、定位问题\n\n### 编程语言支持\n| 语言 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| Python | ✅ 最擅长 |\n| JavaScript/TypeScript | ✅ |\n| Bash/Shell | ✅ |\n| Go/Rust/C++ | ✅ |\n| 其他 | 均可处理 |\n\n### 特色能力\n- **代码审查**: 帮你检查代码问题\n- **重构优化**: 改进代码结构\n- **Bug 修复**: 定位并修复问题\n- **项目构建**: 从零创建项目/功能\n- **API 调用**: 整合外部服务\n- **代码解释**: 分析现有代码逻辑\n\n### 高级功能\n- **多代理编排**: 可同时调度多个 AI 代理协同工作\n- **子进程管理**: 后台运行、轮询、交互\n- **定时任务**: 通过 cron 设置定时执行\n- **跨会话协作**: 与其他会话通信\n\n---\n\n想测试哪方面？比如：\n1. 写一个 Python 脚本\n2. 修复某个 bug\n3. 解释一段代码\n4. 创建一个小项目\n\n直接说需求即可 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":11422,"output":338,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775362561699,"responseId":"019d5bda4d83f862946ee5cc20bccd5c"}}
