{"type":"message","id":"7341a901","parentId":"d683566c","timestamp":"2026-04-05T05:13:34.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I have installed the clawhub and github skills. Let me check what skills are available and which ones are related to clawhub and github.\n\nLooking at my available_skills list, I can see:\n- clawhub - \"Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com\"\n- gh-issues - \"Fetch GitHub issues, spawn sub-agents to implement fixes and open PRs\"\n\nBoth seem to be installed. Let me verify by checking if they're in the list - yes, both are present in my available_skills.\n\nI should answer the user directly about this.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n有的！这两个技能都已安装：\n\n| 技能 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| **clawhub** | 搜索、安装、更新、发布技能到 clawhub.com |\n| **gh-issues** | 获取 GitHub issues、生成修复 PR、审查评论 |\n\n### 快速使用\n\n```bash\n# 安装新技能\nclawhub install <skill-name>\n\n# 搜索技能\nclawhub search <关键词>\n\n# 更新已安装技能\nclawhub update\n\n# 发布技能\nclawhub publish <path>\n```\n\n```bash\n# GitHub issues 操作\n/gh-issues owner/repo --label bug --limit 5\n/gh-issues owner/repo --fork user/repo  # fork 并修复\n/gh-issues --watch --interval 5  # 监听新 issue\n```\n\n需要我用它们做点什么吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":15131,"output":307,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15694,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775365996529,"responseId":"019d5c0f396bf9cd717f8d4a132a843d"}}
