{"type":"message","id":"a837ec32","parentId":"854d06d3","timestamp":"2026-04-05T05:18:23.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking again \"执行任务前应该干什么\" (What should be done before executing a task?). I already answered this earlier - it's about task complexity assessment using the task-weight-estimator skill.\n\nThe user might be testing if I remember things or they want me to demonstrate the workflow properly.\n\nLet me re-answer the question - reminding them about task complexity assessment before executing any task.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n根据规范，**执行任务前必须先评估任务复杂度**！\n\n```\n收到任务 → 自动评分(0-6分) → 根据分数选择执行策略\n```\n\n### 评分表\n\n| 维度 | 0-3分 |\n|------|-------|\n| 复杂度 | 命令/代码量 |\n| 不确定性 | 网络请求/外部依赖 |\n\n### 路由规则\n\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 0-1 | 直接执行 | 30s |\n| 2-3 | 拆步骤存档 | 60s/步 |\n| 4-5 | spawn 子代理 | 60-300s |\n| 6 | 多子代理并行 | 各自独立 |\n\n---\n\n所以现在如果有任务给我，我会先用 `task-weight-estimator` 自动评分，再决定怎么做。有什么任务要给我吗？🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1194,"output":262,"cacheRead":15872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17328,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775366288639,"responseId":"019d5c13ac94184a1d03d871a7dd80a2"}}
