{"type":"message","id":"ba3ee184","parentId":"88033549","timestamp":"2026-04-05T05:55:29.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次问执行任务前应该做什么。这是在测试我是否记住了规则。根据 AGENTS.md，我已经把规则写进去了。直接给出答案即可。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n执行任务前 **必须先评估任务复杂度**！\n\n```\n收到任务 → 自动评分(0-6分) → 选择执行策略\n```\n\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 0-1 | 直接执行 | 30s |\n| 2-3 | 拆步骤存档 | 60s/步 |\n| 4-5 | spawn 子代理 | 60-300s |\n| 6 | 多子代理并行 | 各自独立 |\n\n评分维度：复杂度(0-3) + 不确定性(0-3) = 总分(0-6)\n\n---\n\n规则已写进 AGENTS.md，下次直接执行 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":605,"output":176,"cacheRead":26240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27021,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775368518554,"responseId":"019d5c35b85913e25caa866be07e1f87"}}
{"type":"message","id":"979cdeea","parentId":"ba3ee184","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:02:26.633Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-04-05 14:02 GMT+8] 学习：\n\n> 整合 **任务评分路由**、**上下文保护**（自动压缩）、**子代理进度上报** 三大能力，形成一个完整的、可即插即用的 OpenClaw 技能。 \n> 经过多轮自我审查修正，在科学性、鲁棒性、灵活性、可嵌入性、效率性五个维度达到最优平衡。\n\n---\n\n## 一、技能概述\n\n- **技能名称**：`task_orchestrator`\n- **触发时机**：\n - 每次用户消息（自动记录上下文）\n - 每次 AI 回复（自动记录上下文）\n - 每次任务提交（自动评分、路由、执行）\n- **核心功能**：\n 1. **任务评分路由**：基于复杂度和不确定性计算总分（0‑6），选择 DIRECT / STEP_ARCHIVE / SPAWN_SUBAGENT / MULTI_SUBAGENT。\n 2. **上下文保护**：维护消息队列，超过阈值（消息数、字符数、Token 比例）自动压缩并写入长期记忆。\n 3. **子代理进度上报**：捕获子代理的 `[PROGRESS]` 标记，实时转发给用户，并有心跳兜底。\n\n---\n\n## 二、整体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ OpenClaw 主进程 │\n│ ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐│\n│ │ task_orchestrator 技能 ││\n│ │ ┌───────────────┐ ┌───────────────┐ ┌─────────────┐ ││\n│ │ │ 上下文保护模块 │ │ 评分路由模块 │ │ 子代理执行器│ ││\n│ │ │ - 消息队列 │ │ - 复杂度评估 │ │ - 进度解析 │ ││\n│ │ │ - 自动压缩 │ │ - 不确定性 │ │ - 心跳 │ ││\n│ │ │ - 记忆存储 │ │ - 路由决策 │ │ - 超时/重试 │ ││\n│ │ └───────────────┘ └───────────────┘ └─────────────┘ ││\n│ └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘│\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、完整伪代码（可直接落地）\n\n```javascript\n// ~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator.js\n// ========================= 配置（支持环境变量覆盖） =========================\nconst CONFIG = {\n // 评分路由\n complexityThresholds: [1, 5, 10], // 命令数分界点 → 0,1,2,3分\n uncertaintyPatterns: {\n network: /\\b(curl|wget|npm install|pip install|git clone|docker pull)\\b/,\n interactive: /\\b(input|read|prompt)\\b/,\n localApi: /(localhost|127\\.0\\.0\\.1|\\.test\\.com)/\n },\n directTimeout: 30, // 直接执行超时（秒）\n stepTimeout: 60, // 步骤超时（秒）\n subagentBaseTimeout: 60, // 子代理基础超时 = 总分 × 60\n multiSubagentTimeout: 300, // 多子代理并行超时（秒）\n \n // 上下文保护\n contextMsgThreshold: 50,\n contextCharThreshold: 102400, // 100 KB\n contextTokenRatio: 0.8,\n contextTokenLimit: 131072, // 128K\n contextCooldownSec: 120,\n \n // 子代理进度\n progressMinIntervalMs: 1000,\n progressHeartbeatMs: 30000,\n noOutputTimeoutMs: 30000,\n forwardNonProgress: true,\n \n // 资源限制\n memoryLimitMB: 2048,\n};\n\n// ========================= 工具函数 =========================\nfunction log(level, msg, meta = {}) {\n console[level](`[TaskOrchestrator] ${msg}`, meta);\n}\n\n// ========================= 模块1：任务评分路由 =========================\nconst scoring = {\n computeComplexity(taskSpec) {\n const cmdCount = (taskSpec.match(/&&|;|\\n/g) || []).length + 1;\n if (cmdCount <= CONFIG.complexityThresholds[0]) return 0;\n if (cmdCount <= CONFIG.complexityThresholds[1]) return 1;\n if (cmdCount <= CONFIG.complexityThresholds[2]) return 2;\n return 3;\n },\n computeUncertainty(taskSpec) {\n if (CONFIG.uncertaintyPatterns.network.test(taskSpec)) return 2;\n if (CONFIG.uncertaintyPatterns.interactive.test(taskSpec)) return 3;\n if (CONFIG.uncertaintyPatterns.localApi.test(taskSpec)) return 1;\n return 0;\n },\n route(score) {\n if (score <= 1) return { mode: 'DIRECT', timeoutSec: CONFIG.directTimeout, checkpoint: false };\n if (score <= 3) return { mode: 'STEP_ARCHIVE', stepTimeoutSec: CONFIG.stepTimeout, checkpoint: true };\n if (score <= 5) {\n const timeoutSec = Math.max(CONFIG.subagentBaseTimeout, score * CONFIG.subagentBaseTimeout);\n return { mode: 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec, checkpoint: false };\n }\n return { mode: 'MULTI_SUBAGENT', timeoutSec: CONFIG.multiSubagentTimeout, checkpoint: false };\n }\n};\n\n// ========================= 模块2：上下文保护 =========================\nclass ContextProtector {\n constructor() {\n this.messages = [];\n this.totalChars = 0;\n this.totalTokens = 0;\n this.lastSummarize = 0;\n this.memoryStore = null; // 可注入长期记忆接口\n }\n\n setMemoryStore(store) { this.memoryStore = store; }\n\n estimateTokens(text) {\n const ch = (text.match(/[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/g) || []).length;\n const other = text.length - ch;\n return Math.ceil(ch / 1.5 + other / 4);\n }\n\n async addMessage(role, content, taskId = null) {\n const tokens = this.estimateTokens(content);\n this.messages.push({ role, content, timestamp: Date.now(), taskId, tokens });\n this.totalChars += content.length;\n this.totalTokens += tokens;\n if (this.shouldSummarize()) await this.summarize();\n }\n\n shouldSummarize() {\n const now = Date.now();\n if (now - this.lastSummarize < CONFIG.contextCooldownSec * 1000) return false;\n if (this.messages.length >= CONFIG.contextMsgThreshold) return true;\n if (this.totalChars >= CONFIG.contextCharThreshold) return true;\n if (this.totalTokens / CONFIG.contextTokenLimit >= CONFIG.contextTokenRatio) return true;\n return false;\n }\n\n async summarize() {\n const toSummarize = this.messages.slice(0, -10);\n let summary;\n try {\n summary = await this.callSummarizeAPI(toSummarize.map(m => m.content).join('\\n'));\n } catch (err) {\n summary = this.extractKeyInfo(toSummarize);\n }\n let memoryId = null;\n if (this.memoryStore) {\n memoryId = await this.memoryStore.add({\n type: 'conversation_summary',\n content: summary,\n relatedTasks: [...new Set(toSummarize.map(m => m.taskId).filter(Boolean))],\n timestamp: Date.now()\n });\n }\n this.messages = [\n { role: 'system', content: `[历史摘要已存储，ID: ${memoryId || 'local'}]`, tokens: 0 },\n ...this.messages.slice(-10)\n ];\n this.totalChars = this.messages.reduce((s, m) => s + (m.content?.length || 0), 0);\n this.totalTokens = this.messages.reduce((s, m) => s + (m.tokens || 0), 0);\n this.lastSummarize = Date.now();\n log('info', `Auto summarized ${toSummarize.length} messages -> ${summary.substring(0, 80)}...`);\n }\n\n extractKeyInfo(messages) {\n const text = messages.map(m => m.content).join('\\n');\n const ids = text.match(/task_[a-f0-9-]+/gi) || [];\n const errors = text.match(/error|fail|exception/gi) || [];\n return `任务ID: ${ids.slice(0,3).join(',')}, 错误: ${errors.slice(0,3).join(',')}`;\n }\n\n async callSummarizeAPI(text) {\n // 实际可调用外部 LLM API，这里模拟\n return `[模拟摘要] 长度 ${text.length} 字符，包含关键信息。`;\n }\n\n getStatus() {\n return {\n messages: this.messages.length,\n chars: this.totalChars,\n tokens: this.totalTokens,\n lastSummarize: this.lastSummarize\n };\n }\n}\n\n// ========================= 模块3：子代理执行器（带进度上报） =========================\nclass SubagentExecutor {\n constructor(sendUserMessage) {\n this.sendUserMessage = sendUserMessage;\n }\n\n async spawn(taskId, cmd, args, timeoutSec) {\n const limitCmd = `ulimit -v ${CONFIG.memoryLimitMB * 1024} && exec \"$@\"`;\n const shellArgs = ['-c', limitCmd, '--', cmd, ...args];\n const proc = require('child_process').spawn('/bin/sh', shellArgs, {\n stdio: ['ignore', 'pipe', 'pipe'],\n env: { ...process.env, TASK_ID: taskId }\n });\n\n let lastProgressTime = 0;\n let lastProgressMsg = '';\n let lastOutputTime = Date.now();\n let heartbeatInterval = null;\n let noOutputTimer = null;\n let timeoutId = null;\n\n const resetNoOutputTimer = () => {\n if (noOutputTimer) clearTimeout(noOutputTimer);\n noOutputTimer = setTimeout(() => {\n if (!proc.killed) {\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] 警告：30秒无输出，可能卡死`);\n proc.kill('SIGUSR1');\n setTimeout(() => {\n if (!proc.killed) {\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] 强制终止（无产出）`);\n proc.kill('SIGKILL');\n }\n }, CONFIG.noOutputTimeoutMs);\n }\n }, CONFIG.noOutputTimeoutMs);\n };\n\n const handleOutput = (chunk, isError) => {\n const text = chunk.toString();\n lastOutputTime = Date.now();\n const progressMatch = text.match(/\\[PROGRESS\\]\\s*(.*)/);\n if (progressMatch) {\n const progressText = progressMatch[1];\n const now = Date.now();\n if (progressText !== lastProgressMsg || (now - lastProgressTime) >= CONFIG.progressMinIntervalMs) {\n lastProgressMsg = progressText;\n lastProgressTime = now;\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] ${progressText}`);\n }\n } else if (CONFIG.forwardNonProgress) {\n process.stdout.write(text);\n }\n if (isError) process.stderr.write(text);\n resetNoOutputTimer();\n };\n\n proc.stdout.on('data', (chunk) => handleOutput(chunk, false));\n proc.stderr.on('data', (chunk) => handleOutput(chunk, true));\n resetNoOutputTimer();\n\n heartbeatInterval = setInterval(() => {\n if (Date.now() - lastOutputTime > CONFIG.progressHeartbeatMs && !proc.killed) {\n const elapsed = Math.floor((Date.now() - (proc.startTime || Date.now())) / 1000);\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] 仍在运行，已等待 ${elapsed} 秒`);\n lastOutputTime = Date.now();\n }\n }, CONFIG.progressHeartbeatMs);\n\n if (timeoutSec && timeoutSec > 0) {\n timeoutId = setTimeout(() => {\n if (!proc.killed) {\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] 超时（${timeoutSec}秒），正在终止`);\n proc.kill('SIGTERM');\n setTimeout(() => {\n if (!proc.killed) {\n proc.kill('SIGKILL');\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] 已强制杀死`);\n }\n }, 5000);\n }\n }, timeoutSec * 1000);\n }\n\n const exitCode = await new Promise((resolve) => proc.on('close', resolve));\n clearTimeout(timeoutId);\n clearTimeout(noOutputTimer);\n clearInterval(heartbeatInterval);\n\n if (exitCode === 0) {\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] 执行成功`);\n } else {\n const isOOM = (exitCode === 137);\n this.sendUserMessage(`[子代理 ${taskId}] 失败，退出码 ${exitCode}${isOOM ? ' (可能内存不足)' : ''}`);\n const error = new Error(`Subagent exit ${exitCode}`);\n error.isRetryable = isOOM;\n throw error;\n }\n return exitCode;\n }\n}\n\n// ========================= 主技能导出 =========================\nlet contextProtector = null;\nlet subagentExecutor = null;\n\nmodule.exports = {\n name: 'task_orchestrator',\n version: '3.0.0',\n description: '任务评分路由 + 上下文保护 + 子代理进度上报',\n\n async init() {\n contextProtector = new ContextProtector();\n // 如果 OpenClaw 提供了记忆存储接口，可以注入\n if (global.openclaw && global.openclaw.memoryStore) {\n contextProtector.setMemoryStore(global.openclaw.memoryStore);\n }\n log('info', 'Initialized');\n },\n\n hooks: {\n // 记录用户消息\n onUserMessage: async (message, userId, taskId) => {\n if (contextProtector) await contextProtector.addMessage('user', message, taskId);\n },\n // 记录 AI 回复\n onAssistantMessage: async (response) => {\n if (contextProtector) await contextProtector.addMessage('assistant', response);\n },\n // 任务提交前评分路由\n beforeTask: async (taskSpec, context) => {\n const complexity = scoring.computeComplexity(taskSpec);\n const uncertainty = scoring.computeUncertainty(taskSpec);\n const score = complexity + uncertainty;\n const routing = scoring.route(score);\n context.routing = { score, complexity, uncertainty, ...routing };\n log('info', `Score=${score} (C=${complexity}, U=${uncertainty}) → ${routing.mode} timeout=${routing.timeoutSec || routing.stepTimeoutSec}s`);\n return taskSpec;\n }\n },\n\n // 对外执行函数（供 OpenClaw 调用）\n async executeTask(task, context, sendUserMessageFunc) {\n const routing = context.routing;\n if (!routing) throw new Error('No routing info. Ensure beforeTask hook ran.');\n const sendMsg = sendUserMessageFunc || ((msg) => console.log(`[USER] ${msg}`));\n if (!subagentExecutor) subagentExecutor = new SubagentExecutor(sendMsg);\n\n switch (routing.mode) {\n case 'DIRECT': {\n const { exec } = require('child_process');\n return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n const proc = exec(task.spec, { timeout: routing.timeoutSec * 1000 });\n proc.stdout.pipe(process.stdout);\n proc.stderr.pipe(process.stderr);\n proc.on('exit', (code) => {\n if (code === 0) resolve();\n else reject(new Error(`Direct exec exit ${code}`));\n });\n });\n }\n case 'STEP_ARCHIVE': {\n // 步骤化执行：此处假设 task.steps 存在，否则降级为子代理\n if (task.steps && Array.isArray(task.steps)) {\n for (let i = 0; i < task.steps.length; i++) {\n await subagentExecutor.spawn(`${task.id}_step_${i}`, task.steps[i].cmd, task.steps[i].args || [], routing.stepTimeoutSec);\n }\n return;\n } else {\n // 降级：当做普通子代理执行\n return subagentExecutor.spawn(task.id, task.spec, [], routing.stepTimeoutSec);\n }\n }\n case 'SPAWN_SUBAGENT':\n return subagentExecutor.spawn(task.id, task.spec, [], routing.timeoutSec);\n case 'MULTI_SUBAGENT': {\n // 分片并行：需要 task.splitStrategy，这里简化演示\n const shards = task.shards || [task.spec]; // 实际需实现 splitInput\n const promises = shards.map((shard, idx) => \n subagentExecutor.spawn(`${task.id}_shard_${idx}`, shard, [], routing.timeoutSec)\n );\n await Promise.all(promises);\n return;\n }\n default:\n throw new Error(`Unknown routing mode: ${routing.mode}`);\n }\n },\n\n // 调试接口\n getContextStatus() {\n return contextProtector ? contextProtector.getStatus() : null;\n }\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、五维分析\n\n| 维度 | 设计点 | 评价 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| **科学性** | 评分基于可量化的命令数和风险模式；超时映射合理；上下文保护使用多阈值；进度解析采用标准标记。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **鲁棒性** | 子代理有心跳、无产出检测、超时分级、失败重试标记；上下文压缩有冷却期和降级；所有外部调用有超时保护。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **灵活性** | 所有阈值和环境变量可配置；支持注入记忆存储；可插拔的分片策略；允许用户覆盖路由。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **可嵌入性** | 单一文件，无外部依赖；通过标准 hooks 集成到 OpenClaw；不修改核心代码。 | ✅ 高 |\n| **效率性** | 进度消息限流（1条/秒）；上下文 token 增量更新；子代理复用同一个执行器；心跳间隔30秒。 | ✅ 高 |\n\n---\n\n## 五、集成到 OpenClaw 的步骤\n\n1. **创建技能文件**：将上述代码保存到 `~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator.js`。\n2. **启用技能**：在 `~/.openclaw/config.json` 中添加：\n ```json\n { \"skills\": { \"enabled\": [\"task_orchestrator\"] } }\n ```\n3. **重启 OpenClaw**：`openclaw restart`。\n4. **测试**：\n - 发送简单命令 `ls` → 日志显示 `DIRECT`。\n - 发送 `curl example.com` → 日志显示 `STEP_ARCHIVE`。\n - 连续发送 60 条消息 → 自动压缩，日志显示 `Auto summarized ...`。\n - 运行输出 `[PROGRESS]` 的脚本 → 用户收到实时进度。\n\n---\n\n## 六、总结\n\n本技能是 **任务评分路由 + 上下文保护 + 子代理进度上报** 的完整实现，具备：\n\n- 开箱即用，无需修改 OpenClaw 核心。\n- 高度可配置，适应不同场景。\n- 生产级鲁棒性，经过多轮自我审查修正。"}],"timestamp":1775368946629}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c8cbae3","parentId":"979cdeea","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:02:35.831Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户分享了一个完整的 task_orchestrator 技能方案。我需要把这个学习内容保存下来，并更新到 AGENTS.md 中。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d5a236abd9b740cf949f3805","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# task_orchestrator 技能方案 (v3.0)\n\n> 来源: 用户分享  \n> 日期: 2026-04-05\n\n## 一、技能概述\n\n- **名称**: `task_orchestrator`\n- **版本**: 3.0.0\n- **三大核心能力**:\n  1. 任务评分路由 (0-6分 → DIRECT/STEP_ARCHIVE/SPAWN_SUBAGENT/MULTI_SUBAGENT)\n  2. 上下文保护 (自动压缩 + 写入长期记忆)\n  3. 子代理进度上报 (心跳 + 限流)\n\n---\n\n## 二、配置参数\n\n```javascript\nconst CONFIG = {\n  // 评分路由\n  complexityThresholds: [1, 5, 10],  // 命令数 → 0,1,2,3分\n  directTimeout: 30,\n  stepTimeout: 60,\n  subagentBaseTimeout: 60,\n  \n  // 上下文保护\n  contextMsgThreshold: 50,\n  contextCharThreshold: 102400,  // 100KB\n  contextTokenRatio: 0.8,\n  contextTokenLimit: 131072,     // 128K\n  contextCooldownSec: 120,\n  \n  // 子代理进度\n  progressMinIntervalMs: 1000,\n  progressHeartbeatMs: 30000,\n  noOutputTimeoutMs: 30000,\n  memoryLimitMB: 2048,\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、路由规则\n\n| 总分 | 模式 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 0-1 | DIRECT | 30s |\n| 2-3 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s/步 |\n| 4-5 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-300s |\n| 6 | MULTI_SUBAGENT | 300s |\n\n---\n\n## 四、五维评价\n\n| 维度 | 评价 |\n|------|------|\n| 科学性 | ✅ 评分量化、超时合理、多阈值保护 |\n| 鲁棒性 | ✅ 心跳+无产出检测+超时+重试标记 |\n| 灵活性 | ✅ 环境变量可配置、可注入记忆存储 |\n| 可嵌入性 | ✅ 单一文件、标准hooks、不改核心 |\n| 效率性 | ✅ 限流1条/秒、增量token计算、30秒心跳 |\n\n---\n\n## 五、集成步骤\n\n1. 保存代码到 `~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator.js`\n2. 在 config.json 启用: `{ \"skills\": { \"enabled\": [\"task_orchestrator\"] } }`\n3. 重启 OpenClaw\n\n---\n\n## 六、行动项\n\n- [ ] 创建 task_orchestrator.js 技能文件\n- [ ] 在 config.json 中启用\n- [ ] 测试四种路由模式\n- [ ] 测试上下文自动压缩\n- [ ] 测试子代理进度上报\n\n---\n\n*本技能是三大能力的完整整合方案，生产级鲁棒性*","file":"/home/ai/self-improving/learnings/task-orchestrator-v3.md"}}],"api":