{"type":"message","id":"a8e2433a","parentId":"f7576059","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:03:22.298Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d5c3d10246ed807704064e93a5c3d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OpenClaw Workspace\n\nThis is the workspace for OpenClaw AI assistant.\n\n## 核心规则\n\n### 任务执行前必做：复杂度评估\n\n收到任何任务请求时，**必须先使用 task-weight-estimator 进行自动评分**，再根据分数选择执行策略：\n\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| 0-1 | 直接执行 | 30s |\n| 2-3 | 拆步骤存档 | 60s/步 |\n| 4-5 | spawn 子代理 | 60-300s |\n| 6 | 多子代理并行 | 各自独立 |\n\n评分维度：复杂度(0-3) + 不确定性(0-3) = 总分(0-6)\n\n### 子代理进度上报 (v2.0)\n\nspawn 子代理时复用进度上报机制：\n- 子代理输出 `[PROGRESS] <percent>% | <step>/<total> | <description>` 格式\n- 主代理捕获 stdout 解析进度标记，限流转发给用户 (1条/秒)\n- 心跳：30秒无输出发送\"仍在运行\"\n- 无产出检测：30秒无输出 → 警告 → 强制终止\n- 相关配置：SUBAGENT_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB, PROGRESS_MIN_INTERVAL_MS 等\n\n### 任务编排器 (task_orchestrator v3.0)\n\n整合三大能力：\n1. **任务评分路由**: 复杂度+不确定性评分 → DIRECT/STEP_ARCHIVE/SPAWN_SUBAGENT/MULTI_SUBAGENT\n2. **上下文保护**: 消息数≥50 或 字符≥100KB 或 token≥80% → 自动压缩写入记忆\n3. **子代理进度上报**: 同上 v2.0\n\n技能文件: `~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator.js`\n\n---"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775369002293}}
{"type":"message","id":"01f8d6e5","parentId":"a8e2433a","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:03:30.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经完整更新了。现在给用户确认。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **AGENTS.md 检查通过**\n\n| 章节 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 任务复杂度评估 | ✅ 0-6分 → 4种执行模式 |\n| 子代理进度上报 v2.0 | ✅ 格式、限流、心跳、无产出检测 |\n| task_orchestrator v3.0 | ✅ 三大能力整合 + 技能路径 |\n\n都已固化，下次启动自动加载 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":32367,"output":101,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32724,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775369002298,"responseId":"019d5c3d16e216c06c3cd11f235b34e7"}}
