{"type":"message","id":"59d9b9a8","parentId":"fd24be1f","timestamp":"2026-04-05T06:08:32.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to create the SKILL.md file and other required files.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5ba5238b027e4a3784db965f","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"/home/ai/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/SKILL.md","content":"# task_orchestrator 任务编排器\n\n> 整合任务评分路由 + 上下文保护 + 子代理进度上报\n\n## 概述\n\ntask_orchestrator 是一个任务编排技能，自动化处理任务执行的全流程。\n\n## 三大核心能力\n\n### 1. 任务评分路由\n自动评估任务复杂度(0-3) + 不确定性(0-3) = 总分(0-6)\n\n| 总分 | 模式 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 0-1 | DIRECT | 30s |\n| 2-3 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s/步 |\n| 4-5 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-300s |\n| 6 | MULTI_SUBAGENT | 300s |\n\n### 2. 上下文保护\n- 消息数 ≥ 50 自动压缩\n- 字符数 ≥ 100KB 自动压缩\n- Token 比例 ≥ 80% 自动压缩\n- 写入记忆库\n\n### 3. 子代理进度上报\n- 捕获 `[PROGRESS]` 标记\n- 限流 1条/秒\n- 心跳 30秒无输出提醒\n- 无产出检测 30秒 → 警告 → 强杀\n\n## 配置\n\n通过环境变量或代码内 CONFIG 对象配置：\n\n```javascript\n{\n  complexityThresholds: [1, 5, 10],\n  directTimeout: 30,\n  stepTimeout: 60,\n  subagentBaseTimeout: 60,\n  contextMsgThreshold: 50,\n  contextCharThreshold: 102400,\n  progressMinIntervalMs: 1000,\n  progressHeartbeatMs: 30000,\n  memoryLimitMB: 2048\n}\n```\n\n## 进度标记格式\n\n子代理输出以下格式会自动上报：\n\n```\n[PROGRESS] <percent>% | <step>/<total> | <description>\n```\n\n示例：\n```\n[PROGRESS] 0% | 1/4 | 开始\n[PROGRESS] 25% | 2/4 | 编译中\n[PROGRESS] 100% | 4/4 | 完成\n```\n\n## Hooks\n\n- `onUserMessage`: 记录用户消息\n- `onAssistantMessage`: 记录 AI 回复\n- `beforeTask`: 任务提交前评分路由\n\n## 版本\n\n3.0.0"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":41343,"output":562,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41905,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775369303811,"responseId":"chatcmpl-dbdc0124-cfba-4eda-ac05-43d7908c8056"}}
